<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 94, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&lt;공감과 광고클릭은 사랑입니다.</span><img border="0" class="txc-emo" src="//i1.daumcdn.net/deco/contents/emoticon/things_28.gif?v=2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 94, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;</span><br /></img></p>
